snippet: The bodies of three infants were found Thursday in a filthy house where four other children were removed by authorities last month, a Massachusetts prosecutor said....

headline.print_headline: Prosecutor: 3 Babies' Bodies Found in Filthy House
headline.main: Prosecutor: 3 Babies' Bodies Found in Filthy House

lead_paragraph: The bodies of three infants were found Thursday in a filthy house where four other children were removed by authorities last month, a Massachusetts prosecutor said.
